  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "=General= A few fairly inconspicuous boulders with some decent problems.\n\n=Directions= 10–15 km north of Rimbo. Take road 280 to Sättraby, follow the road through the village and turn right at the fork. Continue for just over 1 km to a small field on the right, where the main boulder lies at the edge of the woods. There are also some boulders on the left-hand side of road 280, between S Sättraby and Sättraby.\n\n=Sectors=",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:smalsjon-rimbo"
        ]
      },
